<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 16:09:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴勒斯坦西岸居民被控谋杀以色列监狱工作人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-west-bank-resident-to-be-charged-with-murder-of-israel-prison-service-worker/00000191-702e-d1e1-af95-73af8ec10000</link><description>约海·阿夫尼 (Yohai Avni) 在吉文·哈哈达沙 (Givon Hahadasha) 定居点的家中被杀，几周后嫌疑人承认了谋杀案。尽管袭击没有任何政治动机，但这名巴勒斯坦人现在被列为安全囚犯</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 15:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-west-bank-resident-to-be-charged-with-murder-of-israel-prison-service-worker/00000191-702e-d1e1-af95-73af8ec10000</guid></item><item><title>“殉难归来”：哈马斯威胁发动更多自杀式袭击，“工程师”叶海亚·阿亚什 (Yahya Ayyash) 趋于流行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-engineer-yahya-ayyash-trends-as-hamas-threatens-more-suicide-attacks/00000191-700e-dab0-a9b7-f41ebf440000</link><description>阿亚什因在巴以冲突中引入自杀性爆炸而臭名昭著，1996 年被以色列杀害，在特拉维夫发生爆炸未遂事件后，阿亚什再次受到关注</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:37:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-engineer-yahya-ayyash-trends-as-hamas-threatens-more-suicide-attacks/00000191-700e-dab0-a9b7-f41ebf440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队兵力短缺，征召先前获得豁免但认为适合服役的预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-calls-up-reservists-previously-given-exemptions-to-fill-personnel-shortage/00000191-6fee-d7fc-ab93-efff29ba0000</link><description>陆军官员表示，“作为以色列国防军扩大现役士兵人数计划的一部分”，大约 15,000 名士兵（全部在 35 岁以下）已分三轮被征召入伍。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-calls-up-reservists-previously-given-exemptions-to-fill-personnel-shortage/00000191-6fee-d7fc-ab93-efff29ba0000</guid></item><item><title>残酷的回忆：哈马斯在特拉维夫发动的自杀式爆炸是对加沙的回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/a-grim-flashback-suicide-bombing-by-hamas-in-tel-aviv-was-a-response-to-gaza/00000191-6fcc-d1e1-af95-7fcd69fe0000</link><description>哈马斯认为，许多达成协议的提议是一个陷阱，美国将采取以色列拒绝结束战争和从加沙地带撤军的立场</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:04:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/a-grim-flashback-suicide-bombing-by-hamas-in-tel-aviv-was-a-response-to-gaza/00000191-6fcc-d1e1-af95-7fcd69fe0000</guid></item><item><title>国际学生联合会将以色列踢出局：“伊朗、俄罗斯和叙利亚仍然存在”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/intl-student-federation-kicks-israelis-out-iran-russia-and-syria-are-still-there/00000191-6b0b-dc6e-a991-ebff69ed0000</link><description>在没有文件和任何书面决定的情况下，以色列代表被国际医学生协会联合会暂停资格。在此之前发生的事情应该引起人们对以色列在世界地位崩溃的警惕</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/intl-student-federation-kicks-israelis-out-iran-russia-and-syria-are-still-there/00000191-6b0b-dc6e-a991-ebff69ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列针对伊朗大规模窃取秘密数据的战争进行了徒劳的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</link><description>反以色列黑客窃取了大量以色列敏感数据，现在正在发布数十亿字节的秘密和机密信息。由于无法阻止黑客攻击，以色列正在发动一场徒劳的战争来阻止泄密</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方打捞哈马斯囚禁期间被杀的六名人质尸体，亲属猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-retrieves-bodies-of-6-hostages-killed-in-hamas-captivity-relatives-slam-netanyahu/00000191-6ef2-d87e-a9b3-6ffb2b1c0000</link><description>人质在加沙全部死亡，他们的家人指责政府抛弃他们，并呼吁紧急释放其余人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 09:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-retrieves-bodies-of-6-hostages-killed-in-hamas-captivity-relatives-slam-netanyahu/00000191-6ef2-d87e-a9b3-6ffb2b1c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯为何想去加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/pa-leaders-gaza-visit-could-help-on-the-day-after-but-only-if-theres-a-deal-with-hamas/00000191-6cd3-d43c-af93-ffd315780000</link><description>阿巴斯在土耳其议会宣布“要么胜利，要么殉难”几天后，他的办公室请求以色列允许其前往加沙。这样的访问可以推进由多边军事力量支持的巴勒斯坦权力机构治理的战后结局 — — 但前提是以色列撤军</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/pa-leaders-gaza-visit-could-help-on-the-day-after-but-only-if-theres-a-deal-with-hamas/00000191-6cd3-d43c-af93-ffd315780000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对协议表示怀疑，坚称以色列控制加沙-埃及边境；哈马斯批评美国提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article-live/aoc-at-dnc-kamala-harris-is-working-tirelessly-to-secure-gaza-cease-fire-hostage-release/00000191-6d8d-d5f6-abf9-ef8d5d8b0000</link><description>以色列国防军称从黎巴嫩发射了 55 枚火箭弹；一些被拦截，另一些落在空旷地区 ■ 拜登：为加沙停火、人质协议“全天候”工作 ■ 埃及外交部称，停火谈判将于周四和周五在开罗举行 ■ 哈马斯高级官员批评布林肯的加沙提案声称“引起了许多歧义”</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 02:25:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article-live/aoc-at-dnc-kamala-harris-is-working-tirelessly-to-secure-gaza-cease-fire-hostage-release/00000191-6d8d-d5f6-abf9-ef8d5d8b0000</guid></item><item><title>在民主党全国委员会，亲以色列的犹太人在亲巴勒斯坦、共和党努力改变叙事的同时拥抱卡马拉·哈里斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/at-dnc-pro-israel-jews-embrace-harris-as-pro-palestinians-gop-try-to-shift-narrative/00000191-6d2d-d8c7-a3d7-7fff1c160000</link><description>亲巴勒斯坦的民主党人正试图引导哈里斯对以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突采取与美国截然不同的态度，而共和党人则试图将她描绘成受党内反犹太主义边缘影响的人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 00:49:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/at-dnc-pro-israel-jews-embrace-harris-as-pro-palestinians-gop-try-to-shift-narrative/00000191-6d2d-d8c7-a3d7-7fff1c160000</guid></item><item><title>接近内塔尼亚胡的消息人士称，人质交易不会让以色列政府垮台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-wont-bring-down-israeli-government-sources-close-to-netanyahu-say/00000191-6c2f-d87e-a9b3-6f7fc5750000</link><description>即使极右翼部长本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇因与哈马斯可能达成结束加沙战争的协议而退出联盟，总理也不会被迫召集新的选举</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 22:17:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-wont-bring-down-israeli-government-sources-close-to-netanyahu-say/00000191-6c2f-d87e-a9b3-6f7fc5750000</guid></item><item><title>“民主党全国委员会代表种族灭绝和战争”：民主党大会在加沙抗议试图引起关注之际拉开帷幕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/democratic-convention-kicks-off-as-gaza-protests-try-to-grab-spotlight/00000191-6c4a-d281-a7fd-ff7fc9160000</link><description>当民主党试图为亲以色列和亲巴勒斯坦的支持者营造一种大帐篷氛围时，数千人在芝加哥游行，抗议“美国资助的以色列对巴勒斯坦人民的种族灭绝”</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 21:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-20/ty-article/.premium/democratic-convention-kicks-off-as-gaza-protests-try-to-grab-spotlight/00000191-6c4a-d281-a7fd-ff7fc9160000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡任命利库德集团盟友主持 10 月 7 日纪念活动后，死者家属愤怒不已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/bereaved-families-are-livid-after-netanyahu-names-likud-ally-to-head-oct-7-memorial/00000191-6c3c-d5f6-abf9-eebc53900000</link><description>亲属指责政府举办仪式来掩盖其失败。尼利·巴尔·西奈 (Nili Bar Sinai) 的丈夫约塔姆 (Yotam) 在贝埃里 (Be&amp;#39;eri) 被杀，他声称这场没有观众的活动反映了害怕公众强烈反对的“懦弱政府”</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 20:40:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/bereaved-families-are-livid-after-netanyahu-names-likud-ally-to-head-oct-7-memorial/00000191-6c3c-d5f6-abf9-eebc53900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 MK 因声称《黑客帝国》电影是由 Yeshiva 学生编写而面临强烈反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-mk-faces-backlash-for-saying-matrix-movies-were-written-by-yeshiva-students/00000191-6c0f-d3b4-a591-ecff04dd0000</link><description>加利特·迪斯特-阿特巴扬 (Galit Distel-Atbaryan) 声称这部成功的电影三部曲是“基于卡巴拉”，在极右翼 14 频道上播出，引发了一场网络风暴。在一篇澄清她评论的帖子中，她写道：“《黑客帝国》是犹太思想的最深渊”</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 20:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-mk-faces-backlash-for-saying-matrix-movies-were-written-by-yeshiva-students/00000191-6c0f-d3b4-a591-ecff04dd0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：内塔尼亚胡表示他接受美国对加沙协议的“过渡提案”，现在由哈马斯决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/blinken-netanyahu-said-he-accepts-u-s-bridging-proposal-for-gaza-deal-now-up-to-hamas/00000191-6c2d-d5f6-abf9-eead5c510000</link><description>一位外交消息人士称，美国的提议包括内塔尼亚胡可以接受的加沙-埃及问题解决方案。不过，拜登政府官员在闭门讨论中承认，目前达成协议的可能性很低</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 20:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/blinken-netanyahu-said-he-accepts-u-s-bridging-proposal-for-gaza-deal-now-up-to-hamas/00000191-6c2d-d5f6-abf9-eead5c510000</guid></item><item><title>国家检察官建议不要调查呼吁伤害加沙人的以色列部长和议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-advises-against-probing-israeli-ministers-mks-who-called-to-harm-gazans/00000191-6c00-d1ee-afb5-6e39b4a30000</link><description>该建议背后的考虑因素包括自他们“热血沸腾”时发表声明以来已经过去的时间，以及国际法院的听证会。司法部长现在必须决定是否展开调查</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 19:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-advises-against-probing-israeli-ministers-mks-who-called-to-harm-gazans/00000191-6c00-d1ee-afb5-6e39b4a30000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列袭击目标是黎巴嫩深处的真主党军火库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/israeli-strike-targets-hezbollah-arms-depot-deep-in-lebanon-sources-say/00000191-6beb-d87e-a9b3-6ffb75ea0000</link><description>据报道，周一晚间，黎巴嫩各地还发生了至少三起以色列袭击事件</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 18:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/israeli-strike-targets-hezbollah-arms-depot-deep-in-lebanon-sources-say/00000191-6beb-d87e-a9b3-6ffb75ea0000</guid></item><item><title>辛瓦尔和内塔尼亚胡不想达成协议，民主党全国委员会的抗议不会改变这一点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-19/ty-article/.highlight/sinwar-and-netanyahu-dont-want-a-deal-and-dnc-protests-wont-change-that/00000191-6bc5-d3b4-a591-ebfd61440000</link><description>在辛瓦尔的救世主幻想和内塔尼亚胡的政治愤世嫉俗之间，真实的人们的生活悬而未决。他们不会被芝加哥针对民主党全国委员会的戏剧性抗议活动所拯救，但前提是布林肯以某种方式奇迹般地成功完成了他的紧急任务</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 18:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-19/ty-article/.highlight/sinwar-and-netanyahu-dont-want-a-deal-and-dnc-protests-wont-change-that/00000191-6bc5-d3b4-a591-ebfd61440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在加沙汗尤尼斯遭以色列国防军导弹袭击身亡，六名士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officer-killed-six-soldiers-wounded-from-idf-missile-in-gazas-khan-yunis/00000191-6ba6-d034-aff9-fbafb2140000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，一架飞机发射的导弹未击中预定目标，击中了部队驻地附近的一栋建筑，导致士兵大楼倒塌</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 17:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officer-killed-six-soldiers-wounded-from-idf-missile-in-gazas-khan-yunis/00000191-6ba6-d034-aff9-fbafb2140000</guid></item><item><title>尽管加沙，内塔尼亚胡在以色列的民意调查中再次领先。他应该感谢伊朗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/despite-gaza-netanyahu-is-topping-the-polls-in-israel-again-he-should-thank-iran/00000191-6b46-d87e-a9b3-6f7f795d0000</link><description>尽管以色列的外交和安全局势严峻，但以色列总理内塔尼亚胡的民意调查显示出令人难以置信的、甚至是难以忍受的复苏。用冷淡的竞选术语来说，他对加沙战争和旷日持久的人质危机的处理是一个失败的问题——但德黑兰有救赎</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 17:46:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/despite-gaza-netanyahu-is-topping-the-polls-in-israel-again-he-should-thank-iran/00000191-6b46-d87e-a9b3-6f7f795d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>